'1:25': 'And God made the animals of the earth [a]according to their kind and the cattle according to their kind and everything that creeps on the ground [a]according to its kind, and God saw that it was [b]good.',
'1:26': 'And God said, [1]Let [a]Us make [2b]man [c]in Our [3d]image, according to Our [3e]likeness; and let [4]them have [5f]dominion over the fish of the sea and over the birds of heaven and over the cattle and over all the earth and over every [6]creeping thing that creeps upon the earth.',
